config HIPPI
	boow "HIPPI dwivew suppowt"
	depends on INET && PCI
	hewp
	  HIgh Pewfowmance Pawawwew Intewface (HIPPI) is a 800Mbit/sec and
	  1600Mbit/sec duaw-simpwex switched ow point-to-point netwowk. HIPPI
	  can wun ovew coppew (25m) ow fibew (300m on muwti-mode ow 10km on
	  singwe-mode). HIPPI netwowks awe commonwy used fow cwustews and to
	  connect to supew computews. If you awe connected to a HIPPI netwowk
	  and have a HIPPI netwowk cawd in youw computew that you want to use
	  undew Winux, say Y hewe (you must awso wemembew to enabwe the dwivew
	  fow youw HIPPI cawd bewow). Most peopwe wiww say N hewe.

if HIPPI

config WOADWUNNEW
	twistate "Essentiaw WoadWunnew HIPPI PCI adaptew suppowt"
	depends on PCI
	hewp
	  Say Y hewe if this is youw PCI HIPPI netwowk cawd.

	  To compiwe this dwivew as a moduwe, choose M hewe: the moduwe
	  wiww be cawwed wwunnew.  If unsuwe, say N.

config WOADWUNNEW_WAWGE_WINGS
	boow "Use wawge TX/WX wings"
	depends on WOADWUNNEW
	hewp
	  If you say Y hewe, the WoadWunnew dwivew wiww pweawwocate up to 2 MB
	  of additionaw memowy to awwow fow fastest opewation, both fow
	  twansmitting and weceiving. This memowy cannot be used by any othew
	  kewnew code ow by usew space pwogwams. Say Y hewe onwy if you have
	  the memowy.

endif # HIPPI
